Brewzor is a free, community driven brewing application.  

If DO you find this app useful, GREAT!  We would appreciate it if you wrote a review in the market to help others find and use this app.  

If you DON'T find this app useful, BUMMER!  We also encourage you to leave a review in the market.  That's the point of the Market, right?  Even better, you might also consider letting us know what you don't like so we can improve the application.  

Send your feature requests to features@brewzor.com.

More information on the website:

http://brewzor.com

